<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>محتوى محمي</title>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:#0f0f17;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif}
.card{background:#1a1a2e;border:1px solid #2a2a4a;border-radius:24px;padding:48px 36px;max-width:400px;width:92%;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 8px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}
.lock{font-size:64px;margin-bottom:20px}
h1{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#e0e0ff;margin-bottom:8px}
p{color:#888;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:28px}
input{width:100%;background:#0d0d22;border:1.5px solid #2a2a4a;border-radius:12px;padding:14px 18px;font-size:16px;color:#fff;text-align:center;letter-spacing:4px;margin-bottom:16px;outline:none;transition:.2s}
input:focus{border-color:#5865f2}
input::placeholder{letter-spacing:0;color:#555}
button{width:100%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#5865f2,#3b4bc8);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:12px;padding:15px;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:.2s}
button:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(88,101,242,.4)}
.error{background:#2a0a0a;border:1px solid #8b0000;border-radius:8px;padding:10px 16px;color:#ff6b6b;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:16px}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
  <div class="lock">🔑</div>
  <h1>محتوى محمي</h1>
  <p>هذا الرابط يتطلب كلمة مرور للوصول</p>
  <% if (error) { %>
  <div class="error"><%- error %></div>
  <% } %>
  <form method="POST" action="/l/<%= lid %>/verify">
    <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="أدخل كلمة المرور" autofocus autocomplete="off" required>
    <button type="submit">🔓 دخول</button>
  </form>
</div>
</body>
</html>
